```py
>>> from sympy import I
>>> A = Matrix(((9, 3*I), (-3*I, 5)))
>>> L, D = A.LDLdecomposition()
>>> L
Matrix([
[   1, 0],
[-I/3, 1]])
>>> D
Matrix([
[9, 0],
[0, 4]])
>>> L*D*L.H == A
True 
```

```py
>>> from sympy import ImmutableMatrix
>>> X = ImmutableMatrix([[1, 2], [3, 4]])
>>> Y = X.as_mutable()
>>> Y[1, 1] = 5 # Can set values in Y
>>> Y
Matrix([
[1, 2],
[3, 5]]) 
```

```py
>>> from sympy import I
>>> A = Matrix(((9, 3*I), (-3*I, 5)))
>>> A.cholesky()
Matrix([
[ 3, 0],
[-I, 2]])
>>> A.cholesky() * A.cholesky().H
Matrix([
[   9, 3*I],
[-3*I,   5]]) 
```

```py
>>> A = Matrix([[1, 2], [2, 1]])
>>> L = A.cholesky(hermitian=False)
>>> L
Matrix([
[1,         0],
[2, sqrt(3)*I]])
>>> L*L.T == A
True 
```
